{"title":"古巴情思","authors":["李瑛"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":1,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴情思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李瑛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友从古巴回来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带给我一颗石子；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗犷像一把石斧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑厚像一支古老的谣曲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把它放在书桌上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我便看见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崛强的安得列斯的山脊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——这整个古巴的土地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至听到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加勒比海的水声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈瓦那街头摇曳的棕榈，和那田野里布谷鸟的鸣啼……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴，能不能说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它也给我带来一片你的天空："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那绛红的花纹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是你的朝霞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪光的白点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是你亮晶晶的雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每晚，当我坐在桌前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读书，写诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它就对我讲述英雄的故事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它曾被出卖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同自由和它的儿女。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双美国皮靴作命令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条美国皮鞭作法律，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可从那时起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威严的大地呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就懂得了生活的意义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就懂得了自己存在的意义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你磨利了多少复仇的枪刺！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说，过去，当游击队员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战斗中打光了子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头，就是武器。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说，有一名民兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至死仍守卫阵地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他用血在碉堡写出菲德尔的名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那石头，就变作一面抽动的旗帜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传说，在古巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当人民战斗的血滴到地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚，就凝成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗颗坚硬的石子；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——这就是为什么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴呀，你的每一块石头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都蕴藏着火的种子……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我多么珍爱这份赠礼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——这来自古巴的小小的石子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它从地球那边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过茫茫大洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在我的桌面上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅起我多少情思："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄马蒂的号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出征战士的歌曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿山里机器的聒噪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"码头工人欢乐的号子……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都一齐回响在我的生活中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道有什么歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比这更宏伟，更壮丽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴的弟兄们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就像看见了你们高昂的头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从骄傲的瞳人中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感到了你们跳动的脉搏和呼吸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我从中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也得到多少鞭策和激励！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我正沉浸在新年的欢乐里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的祖国的夜空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正落下缤纷的爆竹和花雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我坐在桌前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开新的日历，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，红字的第一页——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴呀，染红它的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不正是你三年前的今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高燃的火炬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是我不禁捧起那石块，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿时，仿佛在我们之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再没有距离，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那山山水水都一齐平伏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那风风雨雨都一齐消失；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我忍不住大声呼喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你好呀，古巴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们虽分住在地球的两端，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却像背脊靠着背脊；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们一起战斗、一起劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来最后的斗争的胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊聒［guā］"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}